  "general_provisions": "This bill modifies the Utah Consumer Privacy Act relating to motor vehicle data privacy.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>applies the Utah Consumer Privacy Act to motor vehicle manufacturers; <hr><ltbullet>requires in-vehicle privacy controls for certain motor vehicles; <hr><ltbullet>exempts certain safety and operational data from consent requirements; and <hr><ltbullet>requires the Motor Vehicle Division to provide information to consumers regarding motor vehicle data privacy rights.",
